episodes.title: What Questions Do We Hope This Trial Will Answer?
episodes.description:
We list some questions we would like answered, then we will discuss your questions with you on the Live next Sunday, June 8th at 4:00pm PDT.

Silver Linings Podcast is a safe place for people to come and hear our family perspective on the Chad & Lori trials, but also to figure out the trauma in their own lives and to find resources to help them with that trauma.

episodes.title: Considering Your Collateral Damage
episodes.description: WARNING: This episode includes a brief interaction with AI about pickleball. If you don't want absolutely any exposure to AI please either skip from 8:00 to 10:00 minutes or just skip the whole episode.

episodes.title: Reactions to AI Alex
episodes.description: Some of you had strong reactions to our brief AI Alex interview. Let's talk about it.

episodes.title: Alex's Collateral Damage
episodes.description: We have begun our shift toward emphasizing collateral damage of the many evil crimes that surround us, including Lori's, Chad's, and Alex's. We need your feedback on this format to which we are migrating. Please!

episodes.title: Silver Linings Going Forward - April 18th
